; Coverage for times.cc: weekly period expression

2024/01/01 Test1
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/08 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --period "every week"
23-Dec-31 - 24-Jan-06           Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
                                Expenses:Food                $10.00            0
24-Jan-07 - 24-Jan-13           Assets:Cash                 $-20.00      $-20.00
                                Expenses:Food                $20.00            0
end test
